<p><span class="anchor" id="p24"></span><span class="c3">{وَاجْتَبَيْنَا}</span> <span class="c4">[٥٨]</span> كاف.<a href="#p24" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p25"></span>{وَبُكِيًّا <span class="c2">((٥٨)</span>} <span class="c4">[٥٨]</span> كاف.<a href="#p25" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p26"></span><span class="c3">{الشَّهَوَاتِ}</span> <span class="c4">[٥٩]</span> جائز؛ للابتداء بالتهديد.<a href="#p26" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p27"></span>{غَيًّا <span class="c2">(٥٩)</span>} <span class="c4">[٥٩]</span> جائز؛ لكونه رأس آية،<span class="c5"> قال عبد الله بن عمرو:</span> الغيّ؛ وادٍ في جهنم.<a href="#p27" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>